 Create a Cookbook
4.1 Generate a New Cookbook
Generate a new cookbook named my_cookbook:

chef generate cookbook cookbooks/my_cookbook
4.2 Edit the Default Recipe
Edit the default recipe to create a file with some content:

nano cookbooks/my_cookbook/recipes/default.rb
Add the following content:

file '/tmp/greeting.txt' do
  content 'Hello, world!'
end
